knowledge_base.extracted_text: # ABC Electronics - Business Knowledge Base ## Company Information **Company Name:** ABC Electronics Sdn Bhd **Founded:** 2015 **Location:** Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia **Business Type:** Electronics Retailer & Distributor ### About Us ABC Electronics is Malaysia's trusted electronics retailer, offering a wide range of consumer electronics, home appliances, and smart devices. We pride ourselves on providing quality products at competitive prices with excellent customer service. ### Our Mission To make technology accessible to every Malaysian household through affordable pricing, expert guidance, and reliable after - sales support. --- ## Product Categories ### 1. Mobile Phones & Tablets - Smartphones (Android, iOS) - Feature phones - Tablets - Mobile accessories ### 2. Laptops & Computers - Gaming laptops - Business laptops - Desktop computers - Computer accessories ### 3. Home Appliances - Air conditioners - Refrigerators - Washing machines - Microwave ovens - Rice cookers ### 4. Audio & Entertainment - Headphones & earbuds - Bluetooth speakers - Soundbars - Smart TVs --- ## Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ) ### Shipping & Delivery **Q: Do you deliver nationwide?** A: Yes, we deliver to all states in Malaysia including Sabah and Sarawak. **Q: How long does delivery take?** A: - Klang Valley: 1 - 2 working days - West Malaysia: 2 - 4 working days - East Malaysia: 3 - 6 working days **Q: What is the delivery fee?** A: - Orders above RM200: FREE delivery - Orders below RM200: RM15 delivery fee -
